Examples:

Installing all project dependencies:

Don't: npm install

Do: pnpm install

Adding a new dependency:

Don't: npm install react

Do: pnpm add react

Adding a new development dependency:

Don't: npm install -D tailwindcss

Do: pnpm add -D tailwindcss

Running a script from package.json:

Don't: npm run dev

Do: pnpm dev

Executing a package binary from the registry:

Don't: npx shadcn-ui@latest init

Do: pnpm dlx shadcn-ui@latest init
